### Create an order
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "cust-124",
  "items": [
    {"productId": "prod-001", "quantity": 2, "price": 29.99},
    {"productId": "prod-002", "quantity": 1, "price": 49.99}
  ],
  "shippingAddress": {
    "street": "123 Main St",
    "city": "Plano",
    "state": "TX",
    "zipCode": "75024"
  }
}